  <section>
    <h2>Early Life</h2>
    <div class="timeline-entry">
      <strong>1950:</strong> Born on September 17 in Vadnagar, Gujarat.
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-entry">
      <strong>Childhood:</strong> Helped his father sell tea at the railway station.
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-entry">
      <strong>Early 1970s:</strong> Joined RSS as a pracharak (campaigner).
    </div>
