    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Major Achievements</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Launched Swachh Bharat Abhiyan (Clean India Mission)</li>
      <li>Implemented GST – One Nation, One Tax</li>
      <li>Digital India initiative</li>
      <li>Pradhan Mantri Jan Dhan Yojana – Financial inclusion for all</li>
      <li>Ujjwala Yojana – Free LPG connections to women</li>
      <li>Successful space missions including Chandrayaan and Gaganyaan</li>
      <li>International recognition and strong foreign policy</li>
    </ul>
